44:16.000 --> 44:18.000
He relied on qualifications,

44:18.000 --> 44:20.000
discipline, professionalism,

44:20.000 --> 44:22.000
and so on.

44:22.000 --> 44:24.000
But he made a decision

44:24.000 --> 44:26.000
without expecting anything.

44:26.000 --> 44:28.000
There was nothing creative in it.

44:28.000 --> 44:30.000
It was just a simple

44:30.000 --> 44:32.000
operative decision.

