are usually made

44:54.000 --> 44:56.000
by a willpower,

44:56.000 --> 44:58.000
a leadership potential.

45:02.000 --> 45:04.000
These decisions are usually

45:04.000 --> 45:06.000
made by first-line managers.

45:08.000 --> 45:10.000
It is a simple decision.

45:10.000 --> 45:12.000
A person makes a table of tasks

45:12.000 --> 45:14.000
for the participants.

