This group usually includes

50:06.000 --> 50:08.000
7-12 people,

50:08.000 --> 50:10.000
which is enough.

50:10.000 --> 50:12.000
The second group is

50:12.000 --> 50:14.000
so-called system operators,

50:18.000 --> 50:20.000
who try to determine

50:20.000 --> 50:22.000
how feasible

50:22.000 --> 50:24.000
a decision is.

50:24.000 --> 50:26.000
On the one hand,

50:26.000 --> 50:28.000
and on the other hand,

50:28.000 --> 50:30.000
how new it is.

50:30.000 --> 50:32.000
So, it is known, new,

50:32.000 --> 50:34.000
and feasible-unfeasible.

50:34.000 --> 50:36.000
The third group is analysts,

50:36.000 --> 50:38.000
who try to analyze

50:38.000 --> 50:40.000
and assess resource costs

50:40.000 --> 50:42.000
from the decisions

50:42.000 --> 50:44.000
that come out

50:44.000 --> 50:46.000
as feasible

50:46.000 --> 50:48.000
from the second group,

50:48.000 --> 50:50.000
and the third group

